Potentially useful engine functions

to fire use:
engine.trigger('OpenExternalBrowser', 'http://playbattlegrounds.com/rulesOfConduct.pu'); 	// Website URL
engine.trigger('DestoryLobbyCharacter', 0);													// Player index
engine.trigger('SetLobbyCamera', 0,0,0,0);





engine.mock('SetLobbyCamera', function (pos) {
	console_log('engine received SetLobbyCamera:', pos);
});

engine.mock('CreateLobbyCharacter', function (slotIndex, isGenderMale, netId, nickName) {
	if (debugSkin) {
		update++;
		resizeSlot(slotIndex + 1);
		slots[slotIndex] = { g: isGenderMale == true ? 'M' : 'F', o: null };
	}
	console_log('engine received CreateLobbyCharacter:' + slotIndex + ", isGenderMale:" + isGenderMale + ", netId:" + netId + ", nickName:" + nickName);
	updateDebugView(slots);
});

engine.mock('UpdateLobbyCharacter', function (slotIndex, options) {
	if (debugSkin) {
		update++;
		slots[slotIndex].o = options;
		console_log('engine received UpdateLobbyCharacter:' + slotIndex, options);
	}
	updateDebugView(slots);
});

            l.prototype.togglePopup = function(n) {
                n ? this.inventoryActions.togglePopup(n.ItemDescId) : this.inventoryActions.togglePopup(null)
            }
            ,
            l.prototype.toggleEquip = function(n) {
                n.InEquip ? this.unequip(n.PartDescId) : this.equip(n.ItemDescId)
            }
            ,
            l.prototype.sell = function(n) {
                this.inventoryActions.sellItem(n.ItemDescId)
            }
            ,
            l.prototype.onItemBoxCommand = function(n) {
                console.log("GOT cmd", n),
                "pop" === n.name ? this.togglePopup(n.arg) : "equip" === n.name ? this.toggleEquip(n.arg) : "sell" === n.name && this.sell(n.arg)
            }
            ,
            l.prototype.togglePart = function(n) {
                var l = this;
                this.inventoryActions.togglePartsFilter(n),
                setTimeout(function() {
                    return l.checkNew()
                }, 500)
            }
            ,
            l.prototype.openCrateView = function(n) {
                this.crateViewActions.openCrateView(n.ItemDescId)
            }
            ,
            l.prototype.openCrateViewByDescId = function(n, l) {
                l && this.crateViewActions.openCrateView(n)
            }
            ,
            l.prototype.open = function(n) {
                "partdesc.create" === n.PartDescId && this.inventoryActions.openCrate(n.ItemDescId)
            }
            ,
            l.prototype.pageback = function() {
                this.goto.emit("skin")
            }
            ,
            l.prototype.checkNew = function() {
                console.log(">>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>> checking new...");
                var n = this.scrollDiv.nativeElement
                  , l = n.getBoundingClientRect();
                this.boxes.forEach(function(n) {
                    n.item.isNew && n.check(l)
                })
            }
            ,
            l.prototype.onscrolled = function(n) {
                this.checkNew()
            }
            ,
            l.prototype.ngAfterViewInit = function() {
                this.viewInitialized = !0,
                this.checkNew()
            }
            ,
            l.prototype.trackByItem = function(n, l) {
                return l.ItemDescId
            }
            ,
            l.prototype.trackByPart = function(n, l) {
                return l.partDescId
            }
            ,
            l.prototype.itemExchanged = function(n, l) {
                var t = this;
                setTimeout(function() {
                    n ? ("sell" === l ? t.systemActions.setMessage("Exchanged item for BP") : "open" === l && t.systemActions.setMessage("Crate opened"),
                    setTimeout(function() {
                        return t.checkNew()
                    }, 500)) : "sell" === l ? t.systemActions.setMessage("Failed to exchange item for BP") : "open" === l && t.systemActions.setMessage("Failed to open crate")
                }, 500)
            }
            ,
            l.ctorParameters = function() {
                return [{
                    type: e.a
                }, {

                }, {
                    type: a.b
                }, {

                }, {

            function n(n, l) {

                this.lobby = n,
                this.ngRedux = l,
                this.maxSlotNumber = 4,
                this.skinState = this.ngRedux.getState.skin;
                this.ngRedux.select("skin").subscribe(function(n) {
                    return t.skinStateUpdated(n)
                });
                this.partyState = this.ngRedux.getState.party;
                this.ngRedux.select("party").subscribe(function(n) {
                    return t.partyStateUpdated(n)
                })
            }
            return n.prototype.getPresetId = function(n) {
                var l = o.find(this.skinState.descs, function(l) {
                    return l.Id === n
                });
                return l && l.PresetId
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.getBodyPresetId = function(n) {
                var l = o.find(this.skinState.descs, function(l) {
                    return l.Id === n
                });
                return l && l.BodyPresetId
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.updateMainCharacter = function(n) {
                if (null == n || !this.skinState)
                    return void console.error("INVALID skin state ", this.skinState);
                var l = n.Presets.split(":");
                this.lobby.setCharacter(l[0], l[1], l[2], l[3], "", "")
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.updateSkinCharacter = function(n) {
                if (null == n || !this.skinState || !this.skinState.valid)
                    return void console.error("INVALID skin state ", this.skinState);
                var l = this.getPresetId(n.Hair)
                  , t = this.getPresetId(n.Face)
                  , e = this.getBodyPresetId(n.Face);
                this.lobby.setSkinCharacter(n.Gender, l, t, e, "", "")
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.onSkinUpdated = function(n) {
                this.skinState && (this.skinState.visible ? this.skinState.valid && this.skinState.editing ? (this.updateSkinCharacter(this.skinState.skinData),
                this.lobby.setItems(this.skinState.equipments),
                this.lobby.useSkinCharacter()) : this.skinState.origSkinData ? (this.updateMainCharacter(this.skinState.origSkinData),
                this.lobby.setItems(this.skinState.equipments),
                this.lobby.useMainCharacter()) : console.warn("=>>>>>> no char", this.skinState) : this.lobby.noCharacter())
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.skinStateUpdated = function(n) {
                var l = this.skinState;
                this.skinState = n,
                this.onSkinUpdated(l)
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.updatePartyCharacter = function(n, l) {
                console.log("updatePartyCharacter", n, l);
                var t = l.Skin.Presets.split(":");
                this.lobby.updateSlotCharacter(n, t[0], t[1], t[2], t[3], l.EquipItemPresetIds.filter(function(n) {
                    return null != n
                }), "", "")
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.deletePartyCharacter = function(n) {
                this.lobby.deleteSlotCharacter(n)
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.updatePartyCharacters = function(n) {
                console.log("UPDATING PARTY CHARS ===========================================>>>");
                var l = 1;
                if (null != this.partyState)
                    for (var t = 0; t < this.partyState.partyMates.length; t++) {
                        var e = this.partyState.partyMates[t];
                        this.updatePartyCharacter(l, e),
                        l++
                    }
                for (var t = l; t < this.maxSlotNumber; t++)
                    this.deletePartyCharacter(t)
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.partyStateUpdated = function(n) {
                var l = this.partyState;
                this.partyState = n,
                this.updatePartyCharacters(l)
            }

                return [{
                    type: u.a
                }, {
                    type: e.NgRedux
                }]
            }

                        console.error(n)
                    }
                })
            }

                }).catch(function(l) {
                    return n.helper.error(l, "Matching failed. Try again later")
                })) : void this.systemActions.setMessage("Select game mode type (Solo, Duos, or More)") : void this.systemActions.setMessage("Select region (server)")
            }

                }).catch(function() {

                })

                })
            }

                        l.state = n.createAccount;
                        break;
                    case i.g.NotAuthorized:
                        l.state = n.loginForm;
                        break;
                    case i.g.HasIdentity:
                        l.message = null,
                        l.state = n.createAccount;
                        break;
                    default:
                        l.message = "unknown error (code = " + t + ")",
                        l.state = n.loginForm
                    }
                }).catch(function(t) {
                    "HcServiceUnavailableException" === t ? (l.message = "service is unavailable at the moment. please retry later.",

                    l.state = n.loginForm) : (l.message = "unknown error (" + t + "). please retry later.",
                    l.state = n.loginForm)
                })
            }
            ,

                this.state = n.doing;

                        l.login();

                    case i.h.NicknameTaken:
                        l.message = "nickname already taken",
                        l.state = n.createAccount;
                        break;

                        l.message = "not authorized",
                        l.state = n.loginForm;
                        break;

                        l.message = "account already exist",
                        l.state = n.loginForm;
                        break;

                        break;

                        l.state = n.createAccount
                    }
                }).catch(function(t) {

                    l.state = n.loginForm) : "HcResourceLimitExceedException" === t || "HcConcurrentConnectionLimitExceedException" === t || "429" === t ? (l.message = "servers are busy at the moment. please retry later.",
                    l.state = n.loginForm) : (l.message = "unknown error. please retry later.",
                    l.state = n.loginForm)
                })
            }

            }

            }

                    this.register();
                    break;
                case "NoAccount":
                    this.message = "",
                    this.state = n.createAccount;
                    break;

                    this.state = n.expired) : (this.message = this.source + " authentication failed",
                    this.state = n.loginForm);

                case "ServerBusy":

                        t.message = "servers are too busy, please try again later",
                        t.state = n.loginForm
                    }, 5e3);
                    break;
                case "InMaintenance":
                    this.message = "servers are in maintenance, please try again later",
                    this.state = n.loginForm;
                    break;
                case "banned":
                    this.message = "you are banned from games",
                    this.state = n.loginForm;
                    break;
                case "":
                case null:
                    this.message = "",
                    this.state = n.loginForm;
                    break;
                default:
                    this.message = "unknown login error (" + l + ")",
                    this.state = n.loginForm
                }
            }

                var o

                }

                    console.log(n)
                }
            }

                } catch (n) {

                } catch (n) {

                } catch (n) {
                    console.log(n)
                }
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.onError = function() {

                    console.log("error", this.handler),
                    this.status = n.disconnected,
                    this.connection.disconnect();

                        null == this.handler || this.handler.onError()
                    } catch (n) {
                        console.log(n)
                    }

                        null == this.globalHandler || this.globalHandler.onError()
                    } catch (n) {
                        console.log(n)
                    }
                }

                            i.handler.apply(i, e),

                        } catch (n) {

                        }
                    }

            }

            ,
            n.prototype.accountState = function() {
                return this.ngRedux.getState().account
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.prepareCustomGameState = function() {
                this.ngRedux.getState().customGame.valid || this.invalidateCustomGameState()
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.invalidateCustomGameState = function() {
                var n = this;
                console.log("[INV] invalidating customGameState"),
                this.customGame.getCustomGameState().then(function(l) {
                    n.setCustomGameState(l)
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.startGame = function() {
                var n = this;
                this.ngRedux.getState().customGame.room.isOwner && this.customGame.startCustomGame().then(function(l) {
                    return n.helper.handleResult(l)
                }).catch(function(l) {
                    return n.helper.handleError(l)
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.registerCustomGame = function(n) {
                var l = this;
                this.customGame.registerCustomGame(n).then(function(n) {
                    return l.helper.handleResult(n)
                }).catch(function(n) {
                    return l.helper.error(n)
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.unregisterCustomGame = function() {
                var n = this;
                this.ngRedux.getState().customGame.room.isOwner && this.systemActions.ask("Destroy current match", 5e3).then(function(l) {
                    l && n.customGame.unregisterCustomGame().then(function(l) {
                        return n.helper.handleResult(l)
                    }).catch(function(l) {
                        return n.helper.handleError(l)
                    })
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.unregisterCustomGameOnLobby = function() {
                var n = this;
                this.systemActions.ask("Destroy current match", 5e3).then(function(l) {
                    l && n.customGame.unregisterCustomGame().then(function(l) {
                        return n.helper.handleResult(l)
                    }).catch(function(l) {
                        return n.helper.handleError(l)
                    })
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.updateConfig = function(n) {
                var l = this;
                this.ngRedux.getState().customGame.room.isOwner && this.customGame.updateCustomGameConfig(n).then(function(n) {
                    return l.helper.handleResult(n)
                }).catch(function(n) {
                    return l.helper.handleError(n)
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.setCustomGameState = function(n) {
                this.ngRedux.dispatch({
                    type: "CUSTOMGAME.SET_CUSTOMGAME_DETAIL_DATA",
                    detailData: n
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.setInitialConfig = function() {
                this.ngRedux.dispatch({
                    type: "CUSTOMGAME.SET_INITIAL_CONFIG",
                    initialConfig: e()
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.prepareGameList = function() {
                this.ngRedux.getState().customGame.lobby.valid || this.invalidateGameList()
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.invalidateGameList = function() {
                var n = this;
                this.customGame.getCustomGameList().then(function(l) {
                    return n.setGameList(l)
                }).catch(function(l) {
                    return n.helper.handleError(l)
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.setGameList = function(n) {
                this.ngRedux.dispatch({
                    type: "CUSTOMGAME.SET_GAME_LIST",
                    gameList: n
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.joinGame = function(n) {
                console.log("join", n);
                var l = this.ngRedux.getState().party
                  , t = this.ngRedux.getState().account;
                if (l.inParty)
                    return void this.systemActions.setMessage("Cannot enter custom game when in a team");
                var e = n.PartnerId;
                n.AccountId !== t.accountId && n.Passcord ? this.passcordJoin(e) : this.joinGameEx(e, null)
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.passcordJoin = function(n) {
                var l = this;
                this.systemActions.input("enter password", !0).then(function(t) {
                    t && l.joinGameEx(n, t)
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.selectPlayer = function(n) {
                this.ngRedux.getState().customGame.room.isOwner && this.ngRedux.dispatch({
                    type: "CUSTOMGAME.SET_SELECTED_PLAYER",
                    selectedPlayer: n
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.unselectPlayer = function() {
                this.ngRedux.getState().customGame.room.isOwner && this.ngRedux.dispatch({
                    type: "CUSTOMGAME.SET_SELECTED_PLAYER",
                    selectedPlayer: ""
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.toggleSelectPlayer = function(n) {
                var l = this.ngRedux.getState().customGame;
                l.room.isOwner && (l.room.selectedPlayer === n ? this.unselectPlayer() : this.selectPlayer(n))
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.joinGameEx = function(n, l) {
                var t = this;
                this.customGame.joinCustomGame(n, l).then(function(e) {
                    null == l && "CG:PASSCORD_MISMATCH" === e.Error ? t.passcordJoin(n) : t.helper.handleResult(e)
                }).catch(function(n) {
                    return t.helper.error(n, "Failed to join")
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.leaveGame = function() {
                var n = this;
                this.ngRedux.getState().customGame.inGame && this.customGame.leaveCustomGame().then(function(l) {
                    return n.helper.handleResult(l)
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.toggleLock = function() {
                var n = this
                  , l = this.ngRedux.getState().customGame.room;
                if (l.isOwner) {
                    var t = r.clone(l.config);
                    t.Lock = !t.Lock,
                    this.customGame.updateCustomGameConfig(t).then(function(l) {
                        return n.helper.handleResult(l)
                    }).catch(function(l) {
                        return n.helper.handleError(l)
                    })
                }
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.banUser = function(n) {
                var l = this;
                null != n && this.systemActions.ask("kick user '" + n.Nickname + "'").then(function(t) {
                    !0 === t && l.customGame.banUser(n.AccountId).then(function(n) {
                        return l.helper.handleResult(n)
                    }).catch(function(n) {
                        return l.helper.handleError(n)
                    })
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.moveToSlot = function(n) {
                var l = this;
                this.customGame.moveCustomGamePlayerSlot(n).then(function(n) {
                    return l.helper.handleResult(n)
                }).catch(function(n) {
                    return l.helper.handleError(n)
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.movePlayerToSlot = function(n, l) {
                var t = this;
                this.customGame.forceMoveCustomGamePlayerSlot(n, l).then(function(n) {
                    return t.helper.handleResult(n)
                }).catch(function(n) {
                    return t.helper.handleError(n)
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.moveToUnassigned = function() {
                var n = this;
                this.customGame.moveCustomGamePlayerSlot(-1).then(function(l) {
                    return n.helper.handleResult(l)
                }).catch(function(l) {
                    return n.helper.handleError(l)
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.movePlayerToUnassigned = function(n) {
                var l = this;
                this.customGame.forceMoveCustomGamePlayerSlot(n, -1).then(function(n) {
                    return l.helper.handleResult(n)
                }).catch(function(n) {
                    return l.helper.handleError(n)
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.moveToObserver = function() {
                var n = this;
                this.customGame.moveCustomGamePlayerSlot(-2).then(function(l) {
                    return n.helper.handleResult(l)
                }).catch(function(l) {
                    return n.helper.handleError(l)
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.movePlayerToObserver = function(n) {
                var l = this;
                this.customGame.forceMoveCustomGamePlayerSlot(n, -2).then(function(n) {
                    return l.helper.handleResult(n)
                }).catch(function(n) {
                    return l.helper.handleError(n)
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.clickPlayerSlot = function(n, l, t) {
                var e = this.ngRedux.getState().customGame.room
                  , u = l * e.config.TeamSize + t;
                if (e.isOwner)
                    if (e.players[u]) {
                        var o = e.players[u];
                        this.toggleSelectPlayer(o.AccountId)
                    } else
                        e.selectedPlayer ? (this.movePlayerToSlot(e.selectedPlayer, u),
                        this.unselectPlayer()) : this.moveToSlot(u);
                else
                    e.config.Lock || e.players[u] || this.moveToSlot(u)
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.clickUnassigned = function() {
                var n = this.ngRedux.getState().customGame.room;
                n.isOwner ? n.selectedPlayer ? (this.movePlayerToUnassigned(n.selectedPlayer),
                this.unselectPlayer()) : this.moveToUnassigned() : n.config.Lock || this.moveToUnassigned()
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.clickObserver = function() {
                var n = this.ngRedux.getState().customGame.room;
                n.isOwner && (n.selectedPlayer ? (this.movePlayerToObserver(n.selectedPlayer),
                this.unselectPlayer()) : this.moveToObserver())
            }

            n.prototype.saveIdChanged = function() {
                this.saveId || (localStorage.removeItem("bro_id"),
                this.savePw = !1)
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.savePwChanged = function() {
                this.savePw ? this.saveId = !0 : localStorage.removeItem("bro_pw")
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.getPrevAuthInfo = function() {
                this.id = localStorage.getItem("bro_id"),
                this.id && (this.saveId = !0),
                this.password = localStorage.getItem("bro_pw"),
                this.password && (this.savePw = !0)
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.setPrevAuthInfo = function() {
                this.saveId ? localStorage.setItem("bro_id", this.id) : localStorage.removeItem("bro_id"),
                this.savePw ? localStorage.setItem("bro_pw", this.password) : localStorage.removeItem("bro_pw")
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.start = function() {
                null != this.startTimeout && (clearTimeout(this.startTimeout),
                this.startTimeout = null);
                var l = !1;
                null != this.webSocket.lastCloseReason ? this.onClose(this.webSocket.lastCloseReason) : l = !1,
                this.country = this.region.countryCode,
                this.getPrevAuthInfo();

                null != t ? (this.playerNetId = t.playerNetId,
                l ? this.login() : (this.message = "",
                this.state = n.loginForm)) : this.message = "UNKNOWN AUTH ERROR"
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.check = function() {
                return this.id ? this.password ? /^[a-zA-Z0-9_-]+$/.test(this.id) ? this.id.length < 6 ? (this.message = "ID should be at least 6 characters.",
                !1) : /[\s\t]/.test(this.password) ? (this.message = "Space character is not allowed in password.",
                !1) : !(this.password.length < 6 && (this.message = "Password should be at least 6 characters.",
                1)) : (this.message = "Special characters are not allowed in ID.",
                !1) : (this.message = "Please enter password.",
                !1) : (this.message = "Please enter ID.",
                !1)
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.login = function() {
                if (!1 !== this.check()) {
                    this.message = "connecting...",
                    this.state = n.doing,
                    n.lastId = this.id,
                    n.lastPassword = this.password,
                    this.region.countryCode = this.country,
                    this.setPrevAuthInfo();
                    var l = this.getConnectionUri();
                    this.webSocket.connect(this, l)
                }
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.register = function() {
                var l = this;
                if (!1 !== this.check()) {
                    console.log("REGISTER"),
                    this.nickname = this.id,
                    this.message = "now, creating account...",
                    this.state = n.doing;
                    var t = this.getCredential();
                    this.publicApi.createAuthenticationIdentity(t).then(function(t) {
                        switch (t) {
                        case i.g.Success:
                            l.message = null,
                            l.state = n.createAccount;
                            break;
                        case i.g.NotAuthorized:
                        case i.g.CantUseFamilySharing:
                            l.state = n.loginForm;
                            break;
                        case i.g.HasIdentity:
                            l.message = "userid is already taken",
                            l.state = n.loginForm;
                            break;
                        case i.g.UnusableId:
                            l.message = "cannot use that id",
                            l.state = n.loginForm;
                            break;
                        case i.g.UnusablePassword:
                            l.message = "cannot use that password",
                            l.state = n.loginForm;
                            break;
                        case i.g.IdTaken:
                            l.message = "userid is already taken",
                            l.state = n.loginForm;
                            break;
                        default:
                            l.message = "unknown error (code = " + t + ")",
                            l.state = n.loginForm
                        }
                    }).catch(function(t) {
                        "HcServiceUnavailableException" === t ? (l.message = "service is unavailable at the moment. please retry later.",
                        l.state = n.loginForm) : "HcResourceLimitExceedException" === t || "HcConcurrentConnectionLimitExceedException" === t || "429" === t ? (l.message = "servers are too busy at the moment. please retry later.",
                        l.state = n.loginForm) : (l.message = "unknown error (" + t + "). please retry later.",
                        l.state = n.loginForm)
                    })
                }
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.createAccount = function() {
                var l = this;
                this.message = "now, creating character...",
                this.state = n.doing;
                var t = this.getCredential();
                this.publicApi.createAccount(this.nickname, t).then(function(t) {
                    switch (t.Code) {
                    case i.h.Success:
                        l.message = "success",
                        l.login();
                        break;
                    case i.h.NicknameTaken:
                        l.message = "nickname already taken",
                        l.state = n.createAccount;
                        break;
                    case i.h.NotAuthorized:
                        l.message = "not authorized",
                        l.state = n.loginForm;
                        break;
                    case i.h.HasAccount:
                        l.message = "account already exist",
                        l.state = n.loginForm;
                        break;
                    case i.h.UnusableNickname:
                        t.BannedWord ? l.message = "cannot use '" + t.BannedWord + "' in nickname" : l.message = "prohibited nickname",
                        l.state = n.createAccount;
                        break;
                    default:
                        l.message = "unknown error (code = " + t + ")",
                        l.state = n.createAccount
                    }
                }).catch(function(t) {
                    "HcServiceUnavailableException" === t ? (l.message = "service is unavailable at the moment. please retry later.",
                    l.state = n.loginForm) : "HcResourceLimitExceedException" === t || "HcConcurrentConnectionLimitExceedException" === t || "429" === t ? (l.message = "servers are busy at the moment. please retry later.",
                    l.state = n.loginForm) : (l.message = "unknown error. please retry later.",
                    l.state = n.loginForm)
                })
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.connectionStatus = function() {
                return this.webSocket.status
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.getConnectionUri = function() {
                return this.config.entry + "?" + this.getCredential()
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.getCredential = function() {
                return this.config.bro.replace("{provider}", "bro").replace("{id}", encodeURIComponent(this.id)).replace("{password}", encodeURIComponent(this.password)).replace("{playerNetId}", this.playerNetId).replace("{cc}", this.country).replace("{clientGameVersion}", this.config.gameVersion)
            }
            ,

            }

            }
            ,
            n.prototype.onError = function() {
                this.message = "connection failed",
                this.state = n.loginForm
            }
            ,
            n.prototype.onClose = function(l) {
                var t = this;
                switch (l) {
                case "NoIdentity":
                    this.message = "id or password mismatch",
                    this.state = n.loginForm;
                    break;
                case "NoAccount":
                    this.message = null,
                    this.state = n.createAccount;
                    break;
                case "NotAuthorized":
                    this.message = "id or password mismatch",
                    this.state = n.loginForm;
                    break;
                case "ServerBusy":
                    setTimeout(function() {
                        t.message = "servers are too busy, please try again later",
                        t.state = n.loginForm
                    }, 5e3);
                    break;
                case "InMaintenance":
                    this.message = "servers are in maintenance, please try again later",
                    this.state = n.loginForm;
                    break;
                case "banned":
                    this.message = "you are banned from games",
                    this.state = n.loginForm;
                    break;
                case "":
                case null:
                    this.message = "",
                    this.state = n.loginForm;
                    break;
                default:
                    this.message = "unknown login error (" + l + ")",
                    this.state = n.loginForm
                }
            }
